---
title: Italian Lentil Stew with Cheesy Eggplant, Zucchini and Red Peppers
description: There's nothing like a warming lentil and veggie stew topped with cheesy eggplant to take away the autumn chill. Cozy sweaters and socks are optional for dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-lentil-stew-7b6af422.jpg
